<strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-balthazaar" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1468535); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1468535&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1600571120" alt="Dr Balthazaar" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1468535)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-balthazaar" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1468535); return false;">Dr Balthazaar</a></span>和<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/roget" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1229263); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1229263&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1600571120" alt="Roget" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1229263)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/roget" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1229263); return false;">Roget</a></span><br />
