<div class="scp-image-block block-right" style="width:300px;"><img src="http://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/balths-sandbox/eel" style="width:300px;" alt="eel" class="image" />
<div class="scp-image-caption" style="width:300px;">
<p>一攻击D-4564-14前的SCP-4564-A实例。</p>
</div>
